homosexual, their wives, however, if they had them,  were female.  There were 
medieval kings who divorsed or beheaded their wives; in the SCA the ruler & 
consort are stuck with each other for the reign, and if they decide they cant 
work together, well, everyone has an interesting 6 months.

The private lives of the monarch and consort are, of course, nobodys business. 
 They are not expected or even assumed to be lovers.  (good thing too, because 
