All SCA groups are officially defined in terms of ZIP codes.  Each
groups covers a given set of ZIP codes, and its boundaries are the
boundaries of that region.  The Kingdom Seneschal should have a full
listing of the ZIP codes for each group, so you can probably get all
the info you need from that source.  Most good local maps show ZIP
code boundaries; if not, I believe the post office can supply a
complete map.  

